title: #92Noon! 9a Hour 11/03 - Dean Evason, Mattress Mack, Kevin Gorg
description: PA kicks the show off talking to Wild Head Coach Dean Evason about facing off against the Kraken tonight.  Mattress Mack calls in to discuss the World Series.  Plus, PA & Kevin Gorg break down the 2022 Breeders Cup.
